PakWheels.com (sometimes simply referred to as PW) is the largest automotive classified site in Pakistan. It serves as a online marketplace for car shopping and selling. It also serves as an online community of automobile enthusiasts of Pakistan. As of February 2015, it has 100,000 daily unique visitors. It receives about 45,000 listings a month and 600,000 people take the numbers of car sellers from the website every month.
Started in 2003 as a basement project by a group of petrol-heads to gather all the automotive enthusiasts in Pakistan and discuss the happenings in the automotive industry of Pakistan. PakWheels is the largest community-based automobile website in Pakistan with over 250,000 registered members.
